William E. RUTLEDGE, Trustee in Bankruptcy, etc. v. SOUTHWEST COMPANY, Inc. No. 5800. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Feb. 11, 1958. F. Paul Thieman, Jr., Tulsa, Okl., for appellant. T. Austin Gavin, Tulsa, Okl., for ap-pellee.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed pursuant to agreement of counsel.
